data.title: Southend-on-Sea, England, United Kingdom
data.text:
Southend-on-Sea, fondly known as "Southend," is a vibrant seaside town situated on the Thames Estuary in Essex, England. With its iconic pier, golden sands, and historic landmarks, it offers a charming blend of coastal attractions and cultural heritage.
